{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013bRmcn6yrJGuTMZxzEHrXZ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need. Let me write the migration plan.\n\nSummary of current state:\n- **RabbitMQ**: 3.12.14 (out of support), image `rabbitmq:3.12-management`\n- **Erlang**: 25.3.2.15\n- **Cluster**: 3-node disk nodes (rabbitmq-0, 1, 2), all running, no alarms, no network partitions\n- **VHosts**: `/`, `/app`, `/ops`\n- **Users**:\n  - `admin` [administrator]: full perms on `/`, `/app`, `/ops`\n  - `app-user` [management]: full perms on `/app` only\n  - `ops-user` [management]: full perms on `/ops` only\n- **Policies**: `/app` has an HA policy configured for all queues with automatic sync, while `/ops` and `/` have none\n- **Queues**: `/app` contains `app-queue` and `/ops` contains `ops-queue`, both classic durable queues\n- **Exchanges**: Using standard AMQP defaults with `app-queue` bound to the default exchange\n- **Plugins**: Running prometheus monitoring, Kubernetes peer discovery, and management UI\n- **Feature flags**: All available flags are enabled\n- **Config**: Kubernetes peer discovery enabled, pause_minority partition handling, min-masters queue master locator\n\nThe critical issue is that the HA mirrored queue policy using `ha-mode:all` is deprecated in 3.x and completely removed in 4.0, so I need to migrate away from it before upgrading. The upgrade path requires going 3.12 → 3.13 → 4.0 → 4.1 sequentially, with each step needing specific enablement steps.\n\nMy plan is to first document the current setup, then migrate the classic mirrored queues to quorum queues before touching the version upgrades, remove or replace the ha-all policy, update queue definitions, perform rolling upgrades through each version, update Erlang as needed, and enable new feature flags after each transition. Now I'll write out the detailed upgrade path.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1257,"cache_read_input_tokens":37581,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1257},"output_tokens":23,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"123f0d33-06aa-4216-98ab-776cddb64e3b","uuid":"de20589f-311e-48b0-876f-b570a3e094c8","request_id":"req_011CcQ5n4LSQWmfr2Xfv3Ywu"}
